exorintos-us01-hsxx-{mainos,configos}-0.0.3 (UNRELEASED):
	- [meta-exorint]
		- init-ifupdown: add -f to ifdown to avoid errors upon restart
		- initscripts: /etc/resolv.conf is no longer volatile
		- busybox: enable ADDUSER_TO_GROUP
		- sudo: allow members of group admin to obtain superuser privileges
		- openssh: no longer allows root login
		- ntp: override default bad server configuration and include ntpdate (#8725)
		- xserver-common: patch to avoid listening on all interfaces ('-nolisten tcp' args)
		- nginx: not starting with readonly rootfs (#171)
	- [meta-exorint-enterprise]
		- jmuconfig: (SECURITY): don't bind to all interfaces; fix bad display
		  of services; network field validation and error handling; PoI display;
		  Announcement via Avahi Daemon (#170)
		- encloud, libencloud recipe updates
		- core-image-exorint-min += sudo, net-snmp-server, dnsmasq; data group for data partition - user and admin are members;
		  ntp, ntp-utils, tzdata, tzdata-posix (#8725); bc (for emmc_create.sh); avahi-utils (#170)
		- base: udev rules for new user permissions (#8191)

exorintos-us01-hsxx-{mainos,configos}-0.0.2 (23/12/14):
	- see changes in exorintos-us01-hsxx-kernel-0.0.2
	- [meta-openembedded]
		- openvpn: grabbed recipe from master; fix IPROUTE path (/sbin/ip)
	- [meta-exorint]
		- classes/exorint-version: use DISTRO in human version and added new DISTRO_FLAVOUR to specify image type (e.g. router)
		- linux: added beaglebone support
		- busybox: override syslog-startup.conf, increase syslog size to 1MB and drop duplicates;
		  udhcpc: new resolv.conf generation (appends config generated by JMUConfig)
		- nginx: raise max body size to 15MB for larger flowjs chunks
		- vim: fix warning about undefined license file
		- udev: bbappend with local.rules and udev-cache.default
		- base-files: custom fstab with /mnt tmpfs
		- libencloud/encloud: basic recipes for ECE
	- [meta-exorint-enterprise]
		- classes += router-image-exorint = min + encloud
		- conf: beaglebone machine
		- base: basic regression test script, updated udev config, replace Demo with JMUConfigApp launch
		  split into mainos/configos; overrides for /etc/init.d/rc{,S}, /etc/inittab and xserver-common
		- core-image-exorint-min += openvpn, kernel-module-tun, iptables, tcpdump, rsync, screen
		- epad updated (for image upload and others)
		- jmuconfig updated (general modules wip: system, network, services, management, authentication),
		  css: smaller navbar items to fit HMI
	- [meta-branding-exorint]
		- images += router-image-{mainos,configos}-branding-exorint

exorintos-us01-hsxx-kernel-0.0.2 (23/12/14):
	- Updated the dts files in order to configure the RTS / CTS pins for the uart0 (useful when in RS232 mode)
	- Enable TUN/TAP support as module - required for OpenVPN
	- Added CONFIG_ICPLUS_PHY option in order to support the IP101G eth phy, which is used on latest ECO 507 PCB revision

exorintos-us01-hsxx-{,xloader,bootloader}-0.0.2 (23/12/14):
	- updates

exorintos-us01-hsxx-sdk-0.0.2 (06/11/14):
