exorintos-us01-hsxx-{mainos,configos,kernel,xloader,bootloader}-0.0.1 (10/10/14):
	- new versioning for linux, uboot, images and deploy
	- [bsp] conf: SDKMACHINE="i686" so SDK runs also on 32-bit machines
	- [meta-exorint]
	    - classes: exorint-version and exorint-boottail
	    - linux: dtb files weren't installed to /boot, PACKAGES -= kernel-vmlinux;
	      updated for serial driver fix (RS485)
	    - uboot split into xloader and bootloader
	    - psplash: added mount point /mnt/.splashimage
	    - oprofile: avoid kernel-vmlinux dependency
	- [meta-exorint-enterprise]
	    - conf: DEFAULTTUNE = "cortexa8hf-neon" for -mfloat-abi=hard GCC option
	    - core-image-exorint-min: += nano
	    - base: enable touchscreen calibration, add sbin paths to admin environment
	    - jmuconfig: disable monitoring (used too many resources)
	- [meta-branding-exorint]
	    - split core-image into mainos and configos

exorintos-0.0.1-dev1 (30/09/14):
	- [bsp] bsptool to simplify BSP repo management, build and deploy
	- [poky] exorint branch based on Poky 1.5.3
	- [meta-openembedded] new exorint branch based on dora;
	  picked nginx recipe from master; updated nodejs to 0.10.29
	- [meta-exorint] new exorint layer
		- custom exorint distro without unnecessary poky features
		- uboot: from Exorint repo
		- kernel: from Exorint repo
		- psplash: from Exorint repo
		- busybox: fallback to static address, -= vi, netstat shows programme (-p)
		- init-ifupdown: simplified network/interfaces
		- ifplugd: link up/down detection
		- nginx: PAM authentication module, custom config
		- tar: recipe from openembedded-core
		- vim -= docs, data
	- [meta-exorint-enterprise] new exorint layer
		- base: network defaults and Exorint configuration files
		- epad: from Exorint repo
		- jmuconfig: basic frontend (AngularJS) and backend (NodeJS)
		- jmuconfig-app: Qt-based viewer for jmuconfig
		- core-image-exorint: class based on core-image with X11,Qt and basic dev tools
		- core-image-exorint-min: classes for images with and without X11,Qt
		- other classes: exorint-src for centralized source retrieval specs
	- [meta-branding-exorint] new exorint branding layer
		- core-image-branding-exorint{,-min}: branded image recipes
	      (full-blown and minimal)
